			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Lately, I have been powerleveling a cleric that is now level 45 (brother plays the cleric). I have tried to pick out challenging targets for us to duo, such as Va'Dyn and Rhag1. Bored of leveling, I run to ssra to check if rhag1 is up. When I get to him, he has like 25 minutes left on his corpse. It seems a monk and cleric duo'd him already. Cleric ran there and got a Focus Crystal.
<br />

<br />
We didn't want to leave yet though. We thought we'd attempt a trial run on rhag2. So, after my brother figured out how to get to rhag2 (I've only been there once before) we slowly work our way there. I had KEI and he didn't. We killed the rhag on the left as you come in and then med to full. I run on the ramp - mala - malosinia - send pet in - FBO him (66 air pet). Pet had virtue on him and lost 3/4 of a bub of health on the first round, and the ae went off (275hp/tick, -150 disease resist). Next round he ramped on me twice and I got hit 4 times. I drop down below in the corner, cast heal on the pet, cleric cures and heals me, and I heal the pet again to remove the disease. Throughout that time, pet didn't get hurt at all. So we waited for something to happen, either pet get ripped or Rhag2 to drop below 99%  <img src="images/smiles/eusa_doh.gif" alt="d'oh!" border="0" /> . After about a minute, I run on the ramp again, cast HoE, then SoR. I didn't get ramped on or ae'd. I ran back down in the corner. Rhag2 lost like 2% pretty fast (yay). I waited for them to despawn, ran up on the ramp and casted Sun Vortex. Nuke got 1% from him. Casted again and got another 1%. Ran in the corner. Couple seconds later, "You will not evade me, Phondles!" (cleric). Before I could do anything he died. Then I got summoned and I ran back in the corner. Got summoned again and the 2 rhags in the back aggro'd and killed me.
<br />

<br />
